  ('optician-moex-01579', 'optician', 'optician-moex-109-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關眼睛近反射（nearreflex）的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["眼球向外互相分離，瞳孔收縮，睫狀肌收縮，水晶體變厚", "眼球向內聚，瞳孔收縮，睫狀肌放鬆，水晶體變薄", "眼球向內聚，瞳孔收縮，睫狀肌收縮，水晶體變厚", "眼球向外互相分離，瞳孔收縮，睫狀肌放鬆，水晶體變薄"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "35cf199f6646", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a845aba7a8a1", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01580', 'optician', 'optician-moex-109-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '正視眼測試聚合近點（nearpointofconvergence）正常的結果為下列何者？', '["分裂點（break）在5.2～5.9cm，恢復點（recovery）在10.2～15.0cm", "分裂點在10.4～19.9cm，恢復點在4.2～5.0cm", "分裂點在2.4～2.9cm，恢復點在4.2～5.0cm", "分裂點在4.2～5.9cm，恢復點在4.2～5.0cm"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "35cf199f6646", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a845aba7a8a1", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
