  ('optician-moex-01587', 'optician', 'optician-moex-109-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為他覺式檢查調節幅度（amplitudeofaccommodation）的方法？', '["推近法（push-upmethod）", "移遠法（pull-away/push-downmethod）", "負鏡片法（minuslensmethod）", "動態視網膜檢影法（dynamicretinoscopy）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "35cf199f6646", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a845aba7a8a1", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01588', 'optician', 'optician-moex-109-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一項屬於眼部的低階像差（low-orderaberration）？', '["球面像差（sphericalaberration）", "彗星像差（comaaberration）", "屈光異常", "三葉草像差（trefoilaberration）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "35cf199f6646", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a845aba7a8a1", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "113", "s": "1107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL)
